    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000640/extras/012d35908a690a62ed406062b27f56a2.avif?t=1721062547\" width=620 height=230 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2>The complete collection of Champion skins created over the course of the Rivals Championship Series. These skins feature a dark gray/teal/semi-transparent color theme (depending on the individual skin) with taunts featuring trophies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Special Tournament Collection</h2>These skins were originally created for previous Rivals esports events from 2016 - 2023. We've made these skins available on Steam by popular request, and greatly reduced their individual costs by combining them into packs, so players can complete their collections of past tournament-only skins. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Pack includes all Champion Skins created since 2016 (16 total) excluding guest characters.<br></li><li> Includes Champion Mollo, Clairen, Zetterburn, Forsburn, Pomme, Wrastor, Absa, Elliana, Olympia, Sylvanos, Maypul, Kragg, Hodan, Orcane, Etalus, and Ranno. <br></li><li> Each skin has a unique taunt and look.</li></ul>",
